was the car checked out?

1:12:31.733 --> 1:12:32.757
Yeah.

1:12:32.834 --> 1:12:34.392
All right.
Yeah, thank you.

1:12:34.469 --> 1:12:36.700
Okay.
I appreciate it. Bye.

1:12:38.606 --> 1:12:41.906
Herb's on time, so far.

1:12:46.448 --> 1:12:47.711
All right.

1:12:53.824 --> 1:12:57.693
