lads, let's go!

1:15:44.009 --> 1:15:47.537
Duke, this is Mr. Bradley, head of
the Game Council Athletic Department.

1:15:47.612 --> 1:15:49.671
Yes, sir. It's
a pleasure to meet you.

1:15:49.748 --> 1:15:52.546
It's a pleasure to meet you, couch.
I tell you, I've been following you all year,

1:15:52.617 --> 1:15:54.176
and you've done
a great job.

1:15:54.252 --> 1:15:56.517
Thanks very much.
I appreciate that.

1:15:56.589 --> 1:15:58.580
I wouldn't mind helping
you guys out next season.

1:15:58.657 --> 1:16:03.061
I hear that. I'd like to talk
to the Odin kid, if any way possible.

1:16:03.130 --> 1:16:06.121
<i>Sir, the whole world
would like to talk to Odin.</i>

1:16:06.233 --> 1:16:08.030
<i>Saw him
in the North Charleston semis,</i>

1:16:08.135 --> 1:16:11.902
<i>he lacerated their defense.
Nobody's done that all year.</i>

1:16:11.972 --> 1:16:15.272
<i>- He had some good coaching.
- Bradley: I'd have to agree with you.</i>

1:16:15.343 --> 1:16:17.243
<i>- Let's talk after the game, couch.
- All right, sir.</i>

1:16:17.311 --> 1:16:19.438
<i>He'd sure look good
in that garnet and black.</i>

1:16:20.515 --> 1:16:23.643
- Did you comp his ticket?
- Yes, I did.

1:16:23.719 --> 1:16:25.084
Come on, lads, let's go.

1:16:25.153 --> 1:16:27.088
Come on, sweat it up.

1:16:45.175 --> 1:16:47.006
Hey, mister,
you're all right?

1:16:48.746 --> 1:16:50.042
What the fuck?!

1:16:50.114 --> 1:16:52.343
Do it, Rog.
Do it.

1:16:54.118 --> 1:16:55.312
Fuck!

1:16:58.622 --> 1:17:00.784
Let it go!
Let it go!

1:17:03.762 --> 1:17:05.627
What the fuck, man?!

1:17:05.696 --> 1:17:07.392
What's wrong
with you, man?

1:17:08.900 --> 1:17:10.128
All right.

1:17:11.504 --> 1:17:14.302
No!
Shit! Fuck, Rog.

1:17:14.407 --> 1:17:19.174
It's got to look like
a fucking suicide! Fuck!

1:17:19.245 --> 1:17:22.977
I got him!
Just like you said.

1:17:23.050 --> 1:17:25.518
I shot the fucker!
Now, we do it close.

1:17:25.586 --> 1:17:28.521
No, the cops can tell
someone else shot the first bullet.

1:17:28.589 --> 1:17:31.422
You herbed us, man!
You fucking herbed us!

1:17:31.492 --> 1:17:33.289
You fucking herbed us!

1:17:33.360 --> 1:17:35.886
- Hugo, we have to go.
- Where's the scarf?

1:17:35.964 --> 1:17:37.487
- You know I gave it to you.
- Where's the scarf?

1:17:37.564 --> 1:17:39.692
- We have to go.
- Where's the scarf?

1:17:39.767 --> 1:17:43.168
- Let me get him off the road.
- Rog! Rog! Rog!

1:17:43.238 --> 1:17:46.834
When that car gets here, I'll tell
them you shot him in self- defense.

1:17:46.941 --> 1:17:49.001
He attacked you and
you shot him in self- defense.

1:17:49.110 --> 1:17:51.135
If he wakes up,
he's going to tell on me.

1:17:53.849 --> 1:17:57.547
It won't matter, Rog.
Desi's dead. I'm sorry, bro'.

1:18:08.765 --> 1:18:10.255
What time is it?

1:18:25.150 --> 1:18:26.913
Hold on! Hold on!

1:18:26.985 --> 1:18:30.785
Brandy,
call 911, okay?

1:18:30.857 --> 1:18:33.188
Roger hit Michael with a crow bar
and then Michael shot him.

1:18:49.143 --> 1:18:50.974
- Brandy, help me!
- Oh, my God!

1:18:51.045 --> 1:18:54.139
I need your help!
We need to get him to a hospital!

1:18:54.248 --> 1:18:57.343
Come on, Brandy,
you need to help me, please.

1:18:57.451 --> 1:18:59.420
Come on, Brandy!

1:18:59.521 --> 1:19:00.987
Brandy!

1:19:01.056 --> 1:19:02.182
Fuck!

1:19:55.282 --> 1:19:56.874
I'm sorry.

1:20:07.961 --> 1:20:10.362
I'm sorry.

1:20:12.900 --> 1:20:14.390
Odin.

1:20:44.068 --> 1:20:46.628
I saw Mike with the scarf.

1:20:46.704 --> 1:20:48.433
He's dead.

1:20:48.505 --> 1:20:50.496
He told me
you were with him.

1:20:50.574 --> 1:20:52.599
Now he's dead.

1:20:52.677 --> 1:20:54.440
He's dead.

1:20:56.715 --> 1:20:58.546
Stop. Stop.

1:20:59.884 --> 1:21:02.682
I want to be able
to let you go, but I can't.

1:21:02.754 --> 1:21:06.121
I wish I could,
but I can't. I can't.

1:21:06.225 --> 1:21:09.661
I can't. I can't.

1:21:15.535 --> 1:21:16.661
Shh.

1:21:16.737 --> 1:21:20.070
Shh. Shh.
Go to sleep.

1:21:20.140 --> 1:21:22.608
Shh. Stop. Please.

1:21:22.676 --> 1:21:24.668
Go to sleep.
Go to sleep.

1:21:24.746 --> 1:21:27.374
Go to sleep. Go to sleep.

