- Jason, have you seen Desi?
- Nope.

1:21:32.787 --> 1:21:34.516
- What about Hugo?
- Uh-uh.

1:21:34.589 --> 1:21:36.113
No?

1:21:50.740 --> 1:21:53.106
<i>Desi?</i>

1:21:53.176 --> 1:21:54.108
<i>Desi?</i>

1:21:59.015 --> 1:22:01.040
- Shh.
- Desi?

1:22:12.697 --> 1:22:13.959
Hey.

1:22:19.271 --> 1:22:20.602
They killed him!

1:22:20.672 --> 1:22:23.163
- They killed Michael!
- What are you talking about?

1:22:23.242 --> 1:22:24.174
Hugo!

1:22:24.243 --> 1:22:25.904
