1:22:38.559 --> 1:22:40.652
- You said she slept with him!?
- Emily, shut up!

1:22:40.727 --> 1:22:44.254
- Somebody get an ambulance!
- Fuck off! Get off her!

1:22:44.331 --> 1:22:46.595
- Emily!
- She was a ho'!

1:22:46.700 --> 1:22:49.692
