1:24:15.030 --> 1:24:17.863
Hugo...

1:24:21.403 --> 1:24:22.928
Hugo!

1:24:23.005 --> 1:24:24.529
Sit the fuck down!

1:24:24.607 --> 1:24:28.441
Everybody sit down
and shut the fuck up!

1:24:28.544 --> 1:24:30.876
Now, somebody
here knows the truth.

1:24:30.947 --> 1:24:34.315
Somebody needs
to tell the goddamn truth.

1:24:35.686 --> 1:24:38.712
My life is over.
That's it.

1:24:38.789 --> 1:24:41.815
But while you're
all out here living yours,

1:24:41.892 --> 1:24:45.852
