1:24:54.506 --> 1:24:55.871
But I got played.

1:24:55.941 --> 1:24:58.910
He twisted my head up.
He fucked it up.

1:25:00.012 --> 1:25:02.378
I ain't no different
than none of you all.

1:25:02.448 --> 1:25:04.417
My mom ain't no crack head.

1:25:04.484 --> 1:25:06.349
