1:26:57.639 --> 1:27:01.007
<i>All my life,
I always wanted to fly.</i>

1:27:02.377 --> 1:27:05.370
<i>I always wanted
to live like a hawk.</i>

1:27:17.261 --> 1:27:20.561
<i>I know you're not supposed
to be jealous of anything, but...</i>

1:27:22.200 --> 1:27:23.861
<i>to take flight,</i>

1:27:25.070 --> 1:27:27.834
<i>to soar above
everything and everyone...</i>

1:27:30.375 --> 1:27:32.172
<i>now, that's living.</i>

1:27:36.182 --> 1:27:39.276
<i>But a hawk is no good
around normal birds.</i>

1:27:41.087 --> 1:27:42.987
<i>It can't fit in.</i>

1:27:44.791 --> 1:27:48.319
<i>Even though all the other birds
probably want to be hawks,</i>

1:27:50.097 --> 1:27:52.327
<i>they hate him
for what they can't be-</i>

1:27:54.769 --> 1:27:56.030
<i>proud,</i>

1:27:57.104 --> 1:27:59.130
<i>powerful,</i>

1:27:59.207 --> 1:28:00.730
<i>determined,</i>

1:28:03.878 --> 1:28:05.402
<i>dark.</i>

1:28:08.951 --> 1:28:10.885
<i>Odin is a hawk.</i>

1:28:12.888 --> 1:28:14.753
<i>He soars above us.</i>

1:28:17.860 --> 1:28:19.328
<i>He can fly.</i>

1:28:28.038 --> 1:28:30.063
<i>And one of these days,</i>

1:28:31.141 --> 1:28:33.804
<i>everyone is going
to pay attention to me...</i>

1:28:42.119 --> 1:28:44.883
<i>because I'm going
to fly, too.</i>
